title: Ashanti and Jay Prince Interview
itunes:title: Ashanti and Jay Prince Interview
description:
Today on the show we had the beautiful Miss Ashanti call in where she spoke about the versuz battle with Keyshia Cole, new music, and Valentine Day plans. Also, we had Jay Prince call in where he spoke about new business endeavors, Rap A- Lot Records history, Drake's success and more. And charlamagne had to give PETA a big fat hee-haw after claiming insults like ‘pig’ and ‘chicken’ hurt animals feelings.
